description:
Welcome to Iceland! After a 10 day trip exploring Iceland along the Ring Road, we put together a guide of our full itinerary to help you plan your trip! 

00:00 Intro
01:16 What you need to know
03:34 Day 1 - Starting the Ring Road
04:11 Day 2 - Golden Circle + Landmannalaugar
08:39 Day 3 - Waterfalls + Slheimasandur plane crash
12:38 Day 4 - Reynisfjara to Diamond Beach
16:43 Day 5 - Vestrahorn to Studlagil Canyon
18:44 Day 6 -  Waterfalls + hot springs 
22:05 Day 7 - Oldest Church + Eirksstair Viking Longhouse
24:22 Day 8 - Snfellsnes Peninsula
26:06 Day 9 - Reykjavik Food Tour
27:37 Day 10 - Final day
27:51 How much did it cost?

If you enjoyed this video make sure to subscribe and comment below which country we should make a travel guide for next! 

We can not talk enough about how much we love our Priority Pass.  It has gotten us into dozens of airport lounges and has saved us hundreds of dollars.  Plus its so much more relaxing to be in a lounge. You can get the Priority Pass for free when you sign up for the Capital One Venture X Card. 

If you sign up using our link we will both get bonus points
